      "seed": 751234423,
      "version": 2,
      "versionNonce": 1857768461,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1779241270798,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Table 1 — Physics on PhysXNet\n    Abs scale ↓  25.83 (PhysXGen)  →  11.04 (Ours)\n    Material ↓   1.59             →   0.81\n    Affordance ↓ 3.69             →   1.22\n\nTable 2 — Physics on PhysDB\n    Abs scale ↓  1.08             →   0.37\n    Function ↑   0.36             →   0.83\n    Interaction ↑ 0.34            →   0.96\n\nTable 3 — Part planning (PartObjaverse-Tiny)\n    Voxel IoU ↑  35.53 (no-physics) → 47.66 (+physics, no mask)\n    Full model w/ mask → 53.74   (OmniPart 52.92)\n\nTable 4 — Articulation ablation\n    Joint-Axis-Err-5 ↓\n      Singapo 0.241   Articulate Anything 0.608\n      Ours w/o E_type 0.157   w/o E_kine 0.158\n      Full Ours 0.101   (2.4× better than Singapo)",
      "fontSize": 11,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Table 1 — Physics on PhysXNet\n    Abs scale ↓  25.83 (PhysXGen)  →  11.04 (Ours)\n    Material ↓   1.59             →   0.81\n    Affordance ↓ 3.69             →   1.22\n\nTable 2 — Physics on PhysDB\n    Abs scale ↓  1.08             →   0.37\n    Function ↑   0.36             →   0.83\n    Interaction ↑ 0.34            →   0.96\n\nTable 3 — Part planning (PartObjaverse-Tiny)\n    Voxel IoU ↑  35.53 (no-physics) → 47.66 (+physics, no mask)\n    Full model w/ mask → 53.74   (OmniPart 52.92)\n\nTable 4 — Articulation ablation\n    Joint-Axis-Err-5 ↓\n      Singapo 0.241   Articulate Anything 0.608\n      Ours w/o E_type 0.157   w/o E_kine 0.158\n      Full Ours 0.101   (2.4× better than Singapo)",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
      "baseline": 9
    },
