      "locked": false,
      "text": "1.  Formulation & framework — decoupled VLM-Planning + Diffusion-Realization for physics-grounded 3D generation\n2.  Large-scale dataset — PhysDB, 150k objects with 4-tier physics annotations (holistic · static · functional · interactive)\n3.  KineVoxel Injection — joint-type-conditioned articulation tokens denoised alongside geometry latents in a shared transformer\n4.  Empirical discovery — physics co-prediction resolves part-decomposition ambiguity (mask becomes optional)",
